additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Flammable Solid. Keep out of reach of children. First Aid - If medical advice is needed, contact a doctor or Poisons Information Centre (AUS 13 11 26) and have product pack at hand.

description: Samba Firelighters are the easy way to light your fire. Simple to use, just snap in the wrapper and place amongst kindling, charcoal or briquettes and light. With quick ignition and a long burn time, Samba lights your fire, first time, every time!
name: Firelighters Value Pack
